Part1-How To Generate Allure Reports in Selenium & TestNG
--------------------------------
Steps:
1) Create a New maven Project and Update pom.xml with required Dependencies.
	TestNG 
	Selenium java
	Webdrivermanager
	Allure-TestNG
	
2) Download Maven & Allure Binaries then set path.

3) Check Maven & Allure versions
	mvn --version
	allure --version

Create TestNG Test Cases then run through TestNG.XML

4) Then, run below command in Windows Command prompt:

 allure serve Location of allure-results folder